They've got about 50 people
now doing digital services,

00:42:31.780 --> 00:42:33.140
right in the federal government.

00:42:33.140 --> 00:42:36.140
And they work regular
hours on projects

00:42:36.140 --> 00:42:40.730
that aren't about to kill
the president's major policy

00:42:40.730 --> 00:42:43.500
agenda.

